Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy describes how Melih Arik (hereinafter referred to as "we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects the personal information you provide when using the Dressy application (hereinafter referred to as "the Application").
Information We Collect
When using the Application, we may collect the following types of personal information:
Uploaded photos of users, which may include face data.
Uploaded clothing images.
Use of Collected Information
The information you provide is used exclusively for the following purposes:
To generate AI-powered visualizations of users wearing selected outfits.
To enhance the quality of AI-driven clothing fitting algorithms.
Face Data Information
What Face Data Does the App Collect?
The app processes face data from uploaded user photos. This data includes facial landmarks and other visual features necessary for generating accurate AI-powered visualizations.
Planned Uses of Collected Face Data
Face data is used solely for:
Generating realistic visualizations of clothing fitted onto users.
Improving the performance and accuracy of the AI model used for virtual clothing trials.
Face Data Sharing and Storage
We do not share face data with any third parties. Face data is processed locally on your device and is not transmitted to external servers. Furthermore, face data is stored only on the user's device in an encrypted format to ensure privacy and security.
Face Data Retention
Face data is retained exclusively on the user's device and only for the duration the user keeps the application and their data. The application does not have access to or store face data on external servers or cloud databases. The user can delete their face data at any time by removing the data from their device or uninstalling the application.
Data Storage and Security
Data Storage
Your personal data, including face data and uploaded clothing images, is stored locally on your device. We do not store any personal data on external servers or cloud platforms.
Data Security
We employ industry-standard encryption to protect your personal data while it is stored on your device. This ensures your data remains confidential and secure at all times.
Data Sharing and Retention
Data Sharing
We do not share your personal information, including face data, with third parties. No data is transmitted beyond your device.
Data Retention
Personal information, including face data, is retained only on your device and for as long as you keep the application installed. Once the application is removed or the data is deleted by the user, it is no longer accessible.
Where Is Face Data Explained?
The collection, use, disclosure, sharing, and retention of face data are detailed in the following sections of this Privacy Policy:
Information We Collect
Use of Collected Information
Face Data Information
Data Storage and Security
Data Sharing and Retention
Quoted Text About Face Data
"Face data is processed locally on your device and is not transmitted to external servers. It is stored exclusively on your device in an encrypted format to ensure privacy and security. We do not share face data with any third parties. Face data is retained only for as long as the user keeps the application installed or until they delete it from their device."
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and it is your responsibility to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.
